 oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"center\" padding_top=\"75\" padding_bottom=\"80\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Careers at SRG Technology</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"35\" down=\"0\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As a software and services provider working with a wide range of industries--Education, Healthcare, and Marine Security--SRG Technology is focused on helping organizations become better at what they do, a philosophy we believe applies to us, too. To keep ahead in the fast-moving software world, we need talented individuals who share our commitment to excellence, who help us to keep getting better.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Join Our Team</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Everyone at SRG Technology is an important part of the team. We know that it takes a village to create beautiful solutions, and at SRGT, we encourage creativity, integrity and passion to make our products the best on the market.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We foster a supportive, collaborative work environment, offer competitive salaries and provide room to grow. Contact us today to find out how you can join us at SRG Technology.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Careers at SRG Technology','','publish','open','open','','careers','','','2015-08-19 10:50:16','2015-08-19 10:50:16','',0,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?page_id=40408',0,'page','',0),(40409,2,'2015-08-19 08:21:23','2015-08-19 08:21:23','<strong>Job Duties</strong>\r\n\r\nOur teams are family.  We treat each other with trust and respect. Our solutions promote growth and improvement -- so do we. We want our teams and customers to be productive and happy.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>required Qualifications</strong>\r\n\r\nWe believe that everyone has the right to a career that interests and excites them.  We bring in the best and brightest people with different skillsets from different backgrounds.  We value and support forward thinking and strong work ethics. We think long term when it comes to our employees and customers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Desired Qualifications </strong>\r\n\r\nCollaboration breeds innovation. By bringing unique perspectives to the table, we create unique solutions and address new and exciting challenges. Working together makes us better -- we are more than the sum of our parts.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Additional Information</strong> We thrive on the challenge and creativity of innovating. We don’t quit until we find the best way to solve a problem.  We love taking the complexity of big data and finding the simplicity to drive big outcomes. We definitely fall into the “why not” category of thinkers.','Analyst - Boston','','publish','closed','closed','','analyst-boston','','','2015-08-19 11:06:19','2015-08-19 11:06:19','',0,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?p=40409',0,'post','',0),(40411,2,'2015-09-07 23:33:18','2015-09-07 23:33:18','[vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"grid\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"arrow_back\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"center\" padding_top=\"75\" padding_bottom=\"80\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Careers at SRG Technology</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"35\" down=\"0\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As a software and services provider working with a wide range of industries--Education, Healthcare, and Marine Security--SRG Technology is focused on helping organizations become better at what they do, a philosophy we believe applies to us, too. To keep ahead in the fast-moving software world, we need talented individuals who share our commitment to excellence, who help us to keep getting better.<