5-08-19 11:05:58','About SRGT\n\n<strong>Job Duties</strong>\n\nOur teams are family.  We treat each other with trust and respect. Our solutions promote growth and improvement -- so do we. We want our teams and customers to be productive and happy.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>required Qualifications</strong>\n\nWe believe that everyone has the right to a career that interests and excites them.  We bring in the best and brightest people with different skillsets from different backgrounds.  We value and support forward thinking and strong work ethics. We think long term when it comes to our employees and customers.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Desired Qualifications </strong>\n\nCollaboration breeds innovation. By bringing unique perspectives to the table, we create unique solutions and address new and exciting challenges. Working together makes us better -- we are more than the sum of our parts.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Additional Information</strong> We thrive on the challenge and creativity of innovating. We don’t quit until we find the best way to solve a problem.  We love taking the complexity of big data and finding the simplicity to drive big outcomes. We definitely fall into the “why not” category of thinkers.','Analyst - Boston','','inherit','open','open','','40409-autosave-v1','','','2015-08-19 11:05:58','2015-08-19 11:05:58','',40409,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/40409-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(40441,2,'2015-08-19 22:28:06','2015-08-19 22:28:06','','Solutions','','publish','open','open','','solutions','','','2015-08-19 22:28:06','2015-08-19 22:28:06','',0,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?page_id=40441',0,'page','',0),(40442,2,'2015-08-19 22:29:10','2015-08-19 22:29:10','','Company','','publish','open','open','','company','','','2015-08-19 22:29:10','2015-08-19 22:29:10','',0,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?page_id=40442',0,'page','',0),(40443,2,'2015-08-19 22:57:16','2015-08-19 22:57:16','','Connect With Us','','publish','open','open','','connect-with-us','','','20