rge=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"40468\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"40470\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"10\" down=\"0\"][vc_row_inner row_type=\"row\" type=\"full_width\" use_row_as_full_screen_section_slide=\"no\" use_as_box=\"\" row_box_border_radius=\"\" anchor=\"\" text_align=\"left\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nMassachusetts General Hospital’s Laboratory of Computer Science and SRG Technology jointly developed our premiere healthcare platform, TopCare powered by BlenderTM. TopCare enables continuous outcome improvement and was designed to achieve best practices and meaningful clinical transformations.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nOtisEd is a leader in data management solutions and software development. Trusted by education agencies and companies, OtisEd ensures integrity by upholding the highest standards in business conduct; delivering state‐of‐the‐art integrated, scalable, extensible applications; and exceeding customer’s expectations.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]SRG Technology is proud to partner with Usher’s New Look to offer Music Industry Leadership 101 (MIL101). MIL101 is a full credit‐earning course and blended learning experience aligned with Common Core academic standards and state standards for career and technical education (CTE). Exposing students to more than 30 careers within the music and entertainment industry, MIL 101 opens minds and doors for students who may struggle to find motivation to stay in school.\r\n“Strivers achieve what dreamers believe” – Usher Raymond IV[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"30\" down=\"0\"][vc_row_inner row_type=\"row\" type=\"full_width\" use_row_as_full_screen_section_slide=\"no\" use_as_box=\"\" row_box_border_radius=\"\" anchor=\"\" text_align=\"left\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"40711\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"40712\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"40713\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"medium\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" color=\"\" border_style=\"\" width=\"\" thickness=\"\" up=\"30\" down=\"0\"][vc_row_inner row_type=\"row\" type=\"full_width\" use_row_as_full_screen_section_slide=\"no\" use_as_box=\"\" row_box_border_radius=\"\" anchor=\"\" text_align=\"left\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nInternational Maritime Security Associates (IMSA) and SRGT partnered to create Maritime Alerting Security System (MASSTM), a state‐of‐the‐art, automated threat alert system that provides near real‐time, targeted maritime security threat information to vessels worldwide. Our easy to use and configurable solution allows us to filter and scope alerts to vessels within a determined threat area – providing alerts only when they truly matter. MASSTM increases the prospect of a secure vessel and a secure route while reducing attacks, unwanted boarding attempts and hijackings.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nThe shift away from episodic care to preventative care is now easier, thanks to the strides of SRG Technology’s innovative Population Health Management System, TopCareTM. Joining the ranks of top healthcare institutions across the country, Partners HealthCare has decided that TopCareTM is the ideal Population Health Management System to help them achieve their desired outcomes. With a dedication towards making health care better, Partners HealthCare is using TopCareTM to drive meaningful change, allowing TopCareTM to help them realize their goal of proactive, patient‐focused care.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nQuality Assist, Inc. is an early education company that provides innovative solutions and proven approaches to increase the knowledge, skills, resources, and resourcefulness of all adults who influence the lives, education, and well‐being of young children. With the use of our software, Blender, we have partnered with QA to develop Parentivity, a web‐based community that provides “just right” information when parents need it most. Parentivity captures parent engagement goals and actions then leverages that unique data to deliver relevant, personalized content to help parents confidently care for children from conception to age five.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" header_style=\"\" anchor=\"\" in_content_menu=\"\" content_menu_title=\"\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fa_icon=\"\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"\" content_menu_ion_icon=\"\" content_menu_linea_icon=\"\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"left\" video=\"\" video_overlay=\"\" video_overlay_image=\"\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_image=\"\" background_image=\"\" pattern_background=\"\" full_screen_section_height=\"no\" vertically_align_content_in_middle=\"no\" section_height=\"\" parallax_speed=\"\" background_color=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" color=\"\" hover_color=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"150px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Partners','','publish','open','open','','partners','','','2015-09-17 16:58:01','2015-09-17 16:58:01','',40442,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?page_id=40458',0,'page','',0),(40459,2,'2015-08-19 23:21:46','2015-08-19 23:21:46','[vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" header_style=\"\" anchor=\"\" in_content_menu=\"\" content_menu_title=\"\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fa_icon=\"\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"\" content_menu_ion_icon=\"\" content_menu_linea_icon=\"\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"left\" video=\"\" video_overlay=\"\" video_overlay_image=\"\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_image=\"