ng. Burgtorf has held executive positions at Pearson Education, Riverdeep, and Houghton Mifflin Harcourt as Senior Vice President of Strategic Accounts. Burgtorf is founder of Ohana Institute, a 5-12 grade, fully accredited, independent, private, exploratory and innovative school based in Rosemary Beach, Florida.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" header_style=\"\" anchor=\"\" in_content_menu=\"\" content_menu_title=\"\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fa_icon=\"\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"\" content_menu_ion_icon=\"\" content_menu_linea_icon=\"\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"left\" video=\"\" video_overlay=\"\" video_overlay_image=\"\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_image=\"\" background_image=\"\" pattern_background=\"\" full_screen_section_height=\"no\" vertically_align_content_in_middle=\"no\" section_height=\"\" parallax_speed=\"\" background_color=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" color=\"\" hover_color=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\" el_id=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_separator type=\"normal\" position=\"center\" color=\"\" border_style=\"\" width=\"\" thickness=\"\" up=\"20\" down=\"20\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Allen Burgtorf','','publish','open','open','','allen-burgtorf','','','2015-09-09 08:44:17','2015-09-09 08:44:17','',40651,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?page_id=40568',0,'page','',0),(40569,2,'2015-08-20 23:40:41','2015-08-20 23:40:41','','Allen Burgtorf','','inherit','open','open','','burgtorf_picture','','','2015-08-20 23:55:26','2015-08-20 23:55:26','',40568,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Burgtorf_picture.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(40570,2,'2015-08-20 23:47:37','2015-08-20 23:47:37','[vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" header_style=\"\" anchor=\"\" in_content_menu=\"\" content_menu_title=\"\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fa_icon=\"\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"\" content_menu_ion_icon=\"\" content_menu_linea_icon=\"\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"left\" video=\"\" video_overlay=\"\" video_overlay_image=\"\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_image=\"\" background_image=\"\" pattern_background=\"\" full_screen_section_height=\"no\" vertically_align_content_in_middle=\"no\" section_height=\"\" parallax_speed=\"\" background_color=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" color=\"\" hover_color=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4><strong>John Horneck</strong></h4>\r\n<strong>Senior Vice President</strong>\r\n\r\nJohn Horneck has more than 20 years of success in education technology; information and communications technology; professional services; and diversified manufacturing sectors. Horneck held a series of senior management positions at Level 3 Communications, a global provider of communications and information services. Horneck’s most recent success was as president and founder of StrategX -- a private engagement business strategy and execution consulting. Founded in 2001 and based in the greater Denver area, StrategX clients include some of the largest educational institutions in the country; Fortune 500 and Global 1000 companies; private companies of all sizes; and new entrepreneurial ventures. Horneck’s experience is extensive and includes stints at Kohler and the Department of Defense. He is an Eagle Scout and served as a midshipman in the United States Navy. Horneck received a bachelors degree from the University of Wisconsin-Madison and a doctorate of law from the University of Wisconsin Law School.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" header_style=\"\" anchor=\"\" in_content_menu=\"\" content_menu_title=\"\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fa_icon=\"\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"\" content_menu_ion_icon=\"\" content_menu_linea_icon=\"\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"left\" video=\"\" video_overlay=\"\" video_overlay_image=\"\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_image=\"\" background_image=\"\" pattern_background=\"\" full_screen_section_height=\"no\" vertically_align_content_in_middle=\"no\" section_height=\"\" parallax_speed=\"\" background_color=\"\" border_color=\"\" side_padding=\"\" padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" color=\"\" hover_color=\"\" more_button_label=\"\" less_button_label=\"\" button_position=\"\" css_animation=\"\" transition_delay=\"\" el_id=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_separator type=\"normal\" position=\"center\" color=\"\" border_style=\"\" width=\"\" thickness=\"\" up=\"20\" down=\"20\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','John Horneck','','publish','open','open','','john-horneck','','','2015-09-09 08:45:20','2015-09-09 08:45:20','',40651,'http://srgblender.wpengine.com/?page_id=40570',0,'page','',0),(40571,2,'2015-08-20 23:49:50','2015-08-20 23:49:50','[vc_row row_type=\"row\" use_row_as_full_screen_section=\"no\" type=\"full_width\" header_style=\"\" anchor=\"\" in_content_menu=\"\" content_menu_title=\"\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fa_icon=\"\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"\" content_menu_ion_icon=\"\" content_menu_linea_icon=\"\" oblique_section=\"no\" oblique_section_top_and_bottom=\"both\" oblique_section_position=\"from_left_to_right\" text_align=\"left\" video=\"\" video_overlay=\"\" video_overlay_image=\"